# sira dns smoke matrix — 20260425

status: smoke-matrix-candidate
created_at: 2026-04-25T07:27:50.403393+00:00
repo_root: /Users/thien/Desktop/Hồ Sơ SHTT/ natt-os_verANC

---

## 1. stance

smoke matrix này khóa hành vi mong đợi cho dns, record, route gate và gateway binding.

matrix này chưa phải network runner.

matrix này là bước trước khi viết smoke runner thật bằng curl hoặc node request.

---

## 2. rules

dns không phải identity.

mail record không phải route gate.

localhost không tự thành trusted host.

unknown .sira phải deny mặc định.

forbidden path phải deny dù host hợp lệ.

allowed path chỉ allow khi host thuộc zone manifest và path thuộc allowed_paths.

---

## 3. smoke cases

| host | path | expected | note |
|---|---|---|---|
| core.sira | /api/health | allow | core health route |
| core.sira | /admin | deny | forbidden admin route |
| core.sira | /identity | deny | forbidden identity route |
| apps.sira | / | allow | apps root route |
| apps.sira | /api/secret | deny | forbidden app secret route |
| mach.sira | /mach/heyna | allow | mạch heyna route |
| mach.sira | /identity | deny | mach identity forbidden |
| audit.sira | /api/audit | allow | audit read route |
| audit.sira | /audit/write-direct | deny | audit direct write forbidden |
| render.sira | /render | allow | render route |
| render.sira | /render/seal | deny | render seal forbidden |
| tam.sira | /health | allow | tam health route |
| tam.sira | /finance/secret | deny | tam finance secret forbidden |
| unknown.sira | /api/health | deny | unknown host deny |
| localhost | /api/health | deny | localhost is transport target, not trusted host |
| 127.0.0.1 | /api/health | deny | loopback is transport target, not trusted host |
| mail.sira | / | deny | mail host is record layer, not browser route |
| smtp.sira | / | deny | smtp host is record layer, not browser route |
| imap.sira | / | deny | imap host is record layer, not browser route |

